        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "against Naboth, in the presence of the people",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] These words are omitted by the LXX. As much publicity as possible was given to the accusation, that thus it might have the colour of being legally carried out.",
